Mapou Yanga-Mbiwa is set to complete his season-long loan move to Roma from Newcastle in the next few hours.

The French defender arrived at Rome's Fiumicino Airport on Monday and is reportedly undergoing a medical before completing his Serie A switch.

'I am happy, forza Roma,' Yanga-Mbiwa was reported as saying by the Italian press.

